ades|Tied with ''[[Godless (TV series)|Godless]]''.}}\n|-\n| [[Location Managers Guild Awards#2018|Location Managers Guild Awards]]\n| Outstanding Locations in Contemporary Television\n| Wes Hagan and Kevin Dowling\n| {{won}}\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news |last1=Caranicas |first1=Peter |title='Dunkirk,' 'Baby Driver' Score Motion Picture Wins at LMGI Awards |url=https://variety.com/2018/artisans/awards/dunkirk-baby-driver-game-of-thrones-score-motion-picture-wins-at-lmgi-awards-1202746856/ |accessdate=April 8, 2018 |work=Variety |date=April 7, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[44th People's Choice Awards|People's Choice Awards]]\n| The Drama TV Star of 2018\n| Jason Bateman\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eonline.com/shows/peoples_choice_awards/news/963752/2018-people-s-choice-awards-complete-list-of-nominations|title=2018 People's Choice Awards: Complete List of Nominations|publisher=E! News|first=Johnni|last=Macke|date=September 5, 2018|accessdate=September 5, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| The Bingeworthy Show of 2018\n| ''Ozark''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[70th Primetime Emmy Awards|Primetime Emmy Awards]]\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Lead Actor in a Drama Series|Outstanding Lead Actor in a Drama Series]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Jason Bateman (for \"The Toll\")\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"5\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.emmys.com/shows/ozark |title=Ozark |website=Television Academy |accessdate=August 14, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series|Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Daniel Sackheim]] (for \"Tonight We Improvise\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[70th Primetime Creative Arts Emmy Awards|Primetime Creative Arts Emmy Awards]]\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Cinematography for a Single-Camera Series (One Hour)|Outstanding Cinematography for a Single-Camera Series (One Hour)]]\